item.title: 2020-08-18: English self-learning
item.description: 1. Training-1 trial.1 Who cooked this? I do did. I went to the library yesterday. Does he know where he goes to go? Yes, he does. How long have you lived in this country? Ellen may be angry. Could you take me the salt? or Will you please pass me the salt? Sure. At that time, they started to sing. They began to sing then.
